# Blog Post Structure Guide

## Key Files
- Blog posts are stored in [_posts/](mdc:_posts/) for published content
- Drafts are stored in [_drafts/](mdc:_drafts/) for work in progress
- Writing style guidelines are in [WRITING_STYLE.md](mdc:WRITING_STYLE.md)
- Pending tasks and improvements in [TODO.md](mdc:TODO.md)

